***Product Endpoints***

/product --> (GET) List all product available
/product/id --> (GET) List the product with given product id

*** Category Endpoints ***
/categories/id --> (GET) List the type of category and it's subcategories
/categories/id/products --> (GET) List all products with given category

*** Shopping Cart Enpoints ***
/shoppingcart/id --> (GET) Returns items in cart with given id
/shoppingcart/id --> (POST) request adds a product to cart with given id
/shoppingcart/id --> (PUT) update quantity of product in given cart
/shoppingcart/id --> (DELETE) deletes a product from given cart